title: PHOTOS: Hare, Red Hook set stage for showdown with Spackenkill in MHAL final
text: PHOTOS: Hare, Red Hook set stage for showdown with Spackenkill in MHAL final Stephen Haynes, Poughkeepsie Journal 9:53 p.m. EDT October 20, 2015 Red Hook's Colin Sullivan gains control of the ball as Wallkill's Ryan Castle closes in on him during Tuesdays Mid-Hudson Athletic League semi-final held in Staatsburg. Patrick Oehler/Poughkeepsie Journal Red Hook's Dennis Hare headers the ball into the goal past Wallkill's Jeffrey Arenas during Tuesdays Mid-Hudson Athletic League semi-final held in Staatsburg. Patrick Oehler/Poughkeepsie Journal Red Hook's Zach Sivulich headers the ball past a line of Wallkill's players during Tuesdays Mid-Hudson Athletic League semi-final held in Staatsburg. Patrick Oehler/Poughkeepsie Journal Red Hook's Dennis Hare drives the ball past Wallkill's Corey Scheibling to score Red Hook's fourth goal during Tuesdays Mid-Hudson Athletic League Semi-Final held in Staatsburg.
